                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8576" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0260</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1433 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">责任下天风，发展可持续——天风证券的社会责任管理演进</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Doing Duty Awe-inspiringly，Developing Sustainably -- the Evolution of Social Responsibility Management of TF Securities</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王勇，于晓源，万金艳，张爱武，程先知</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中农业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">施丹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天风证券股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；ESG；公司治理；可持续发展；金融机构；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate social responsibility, ESG, Corporate governance, Sustainable development, Financial institution</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业践行社会责任（CSR、ESG或CSB）应基于对可持续发展、利益相关者共益等理论基础的信仰，秉持三重底线原则，将社会责任管理根植于企业道德文化的土壤之中，并与企业战略、经营深度融合，并同步注重公司治理与组织建设，方可自我驱动、行稳致远。本案例描述了天风证券股份有限公司对社会责任及其管治保障机制的实践与思考。本文首先简要介绍了企业所取得的社会绩效，以及关于责任管理动机的访谈，帮助学习者理解现实中企业践行社会责任的动机及理论基础。接着介绍了企业对社会责任概念本地化的实践探索与优化历程，并重点介绍了企业总结的“三大金融方向”，帮助学习者理解三重底线原则、辨析CSR与ESG等基本概念。然后以天风证券走访慰问、结对帮扶脱贫县房县的故事为例，引导学习者思考CSR为何不只是简单的公益，CSR应如何与企业经营深度融合。再接着，本文介绍了企业为保障责任管理落地而对公司治理、组织建设探索的过程、遇到的问题与优化方案，引导学习者思考如何保障CSR管理落地，培养学习者CSR践行能力。本案例最后还提到了天风证券正在尝试的企业可持续发展商业（CSB）变革，给学习者留下意犹未尽的空间。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The practice of Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR, ESG or CSB) should be based on the belief in the theory of sustainable development and stakeholders, uphold the Triple Bottom Line principle (TBL), root CSR in the soil of corporate ethical culture, deeply integrate with corporate strategy and operation, and simultaneously pay attention to corporate governance and organizational construction, in order to drive themselves and achieve stability and long-term development. This case describes the practice and thinking of Tianfeng Securities Co., Ltd. on CSR and its governance guarantee mechanism. Firstly, this paper briefly introduces the social performance achieved by enterprises and interviews about the motivation of responsibility management to help learners understand the motivation and theoretical basis of CSR. Then it introduces the practice exploration and optimization process of the localization of the concept of CSR, and focuses on the &quot;three financial directions&quot; summarized by enterprises, to help learners understand TBL, and distinguish the basic concepts of CSR and ESG. Then, taking the story of Tianfeng Securities&#39; visit and support to Fangxian County, a county in poverty alleviation, as an example, learners are guided to think about why CSR is not just a simple public welfare, and how CSR should be deeply integrated with enterprise management. Then, this paper introduces the exploration process of corporate governance and organizational construction, problems encountered and optimization plans of enterprises to ensure the implementation of CSR, guides learners to think about how to ensure the implementation of CSR management and cultivates learners&#39; CSR practice ability. At the end of this case, we also mentioned the Corporate Sustainable development Business (CSB) reform that Tianfeng Securities is trying, leaving the learners with more room to explore.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；ESG；可持续发展；利益相关者；三重底线</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
